# Domain Reference

## Entities

- **User** — registers, places orders. Roles: `owner`, `admin`, `user`, `suspended`
- **Organization** — owns listings. Statuses: `created` → `verified` (by platform admin). Unverified orgs' listings hidden from public
- **Membership** — many-to-many User↔Org. Roles: `admin`, `editor`, `viewer`. Statuses: `candidate`, `invited`, `member`
- **ListingCategory** — seed (verified=true, global) or user-created (verified=false, org-scoped)
- **Listing** — rentable item. Statuses: `hidden` → `published` → `in_rent` → `archived`. Editors set `published`/`hidden`/`archived`; `in_rent` is automatic
- **Order** — rental request for a listing

## Order State Machine

```
pending ──[offer]──► offered ──[confirm]──► confirmed ──[auto: start_date]──► active ──[auto: end_date]──► finished
  └──[reject]──► rejected    └──[decline]──► declined    ├──[user cancel]──► canceled_by_user         ├──[user cancel]──► canceled_by_user
                                                          └──[org cancel]──► canceled_by_organization  └──[org cancel]──► canceled_by_organization
```

Terminal: `finished`, `rejected`, `declined`, `canceled_by_user`, `canceled_by_organization`

## Permission Levels

| Level | Requirement |
|-------|-------------|
| Public | None |
| Authenticated | Valid JWT, not suspended |
| Org Editor | Authenticated + editor/admin membership |
| Org Admin | Authenticated + admin membership |
| Platform Admin | Authenticated + user role admin/owner |

## API Route Prefixes

- `/users/` — registration, profile, `GET /users/me`
- `/organizations/{org_id}/` — org management, members, listings, orders (org-side)
- `/listings/` — public catalog browse
- `/orders/` — user-side order actions
- `/private/` — platform admin endpoints (verify org, change user role)

